docs
*.md
!backend/data/ai-ops/skills/**/SKILL.md
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
LICENSE.md

# Reports
reports

# Docker files (not needed inside container)
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# Kiro specs
.kiro

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

